==感情生活==
1998年世界巡迴演唱（{{lang|en|Spiceworld Tour}}）期間，與[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]籍舞蹈員吉米·古勒扎爾（{{lang|en| Jimmy Gulzar}}）共渡愛河，二人很快便結婚<ref name="people">{{cite news|url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20133083,00.html|title=Bitter Season|author=Steve Dougherty|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|date=27 November 2000|accessdate=9 July 2012|archive-date=2017-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404165002/http://people.com/archive/bitter-season-vol-54-no-22/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並於1999年誕下一女<ref name="people" />，婚後媚兒碧曾將她的藝名改為Mel G（從夫姓）。該段婚姻只維持了兩年的時間<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/1027260.stm|title=Mel B settles with ex-husband|date=16 November 2000|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2015-07-13|archive-date=2004-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040512214946/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/1027260.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，媚兒碧雖然贏得女兒的[[撫養權|撫養權]]，但需要給予前夫280萬美元的分手費<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/981109.stm|title=Mel B settles access case|date=20 October 2000|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2015-07-13|archive-date=2017-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170817164957/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/981109.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

媚兒碧曾經與著名美國黑人影星[[愛迪·梅菲|愛迪·梅菲]]（{{lang|en|Eddie Murphy}}）有過一段短暫的感情，並為他誕下孩子，經過一連串法庭訴訟及[[親子鑑定|DNA測試]]後<ref>Lehner, Marla. [http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1566035,00.html "Eddie Murphy Questions Paternity of Mel B's Baby"] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120530/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,1566035,00.html |date=2012-05-30 }}, ''People'', 5 December 2006.</ref>，愛迪·梅菲終同意給予媚兒碧700萬美元的「懷孕的費用」<ref>[http://www.accesshollywood.com/news/ah6332.shtml "Eddie Murphy Admits To Fathering Mel B.'s Baby"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.accesshollywood.com/news/ah6332.shtml |date=20080103090317 }}, ''Access Hollywood'', 4 August 2007. Retrieved 4 August 2007.</ref>。

2007年，她與電影製片人斯蒂芬·貝拉方特（{{lang|en|Stephen Belafonte}}）結婚，婚禮在[[埃及|埃及]]舉行，只請了雙方的家人觀禮，他們的女兒於2011年出世。在長達10年的婚姻中，她多次遭受史提芬·貝拉方得的家庭暴力，在2017年12月，他們10年的婚姻結束。<ref name=people2011baby>[http://celebritybabies.people.com/2011/09/02/melanie-brown-welcomes-a-daughter/ "Melanie Brown Welcomes a Daughter"] {{Wayback|url=http://celebritybabies.people.com/2011/09/02/melanie-brown-welcomes-a-daughter/ |date=20170316005037 }} 2 September 2011, ''People''</ref><ref>[http://au.eonline.com/news/spice_girl_mel_b_reveals_baby/261780 "Spice Girl Mel B Reveals Baby Name—Is It Scary?"] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20141229224621/http://au.eonline.com/news/spice_girl_mel_b_reveals_baby/261780 |date=2014-12-29 }} 7 September 2011, E!</ref>。

媚兒碧向傳媒透露，她曾經與一名[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]女子相戀四年<ref>Simon Hattenstone, [http://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/nov/29/mel-b-x-factor 'I do have a big ego. And I'm in love with myself': an exclusive interview with Mel B] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/nov/29/mel-b-x-factor |date=20201212120050 }}, ''The Guardian'', 29 November 2014</ref><ref>Nick Duffy, [http://www.pinknews.co.uk/2014/11/30/mel-b-i-had-a-four-year-relationship-with-a-woman/ Mel B: I had a four-year relationship with a woman] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pinknews.co.uk/2014/11/30/mel-b-i-had-a-four-year-relationship-with-a-woman/ |date=20200214094605 }}, ''Pink News'', 30 November 2014</ref>。

